snippet.title: Holiday After Special Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Holiday After Special is a slice-of-life, horror anthology following the Step Sisters' adventures over the holidays before the events of Halloween After Special.

Episodes 1 - 4 are now available on itchio!
https://horror-n-oates.itch.io/holiday-after-special
